  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Aquatic Chain showcase emphasizing the Biolume shimmer layer (Surface + Biolume stages). OCEANIC's boid cohesion at low separation creates a tight cluster whose internal light-frequency modulation pairs with the Biolume half-wave rectifier shimmer. Fathom at Character 0.55 (balanced, tilting bright). Drift at 2 voices — minimal spread so the bioluminescent quality is not smeared. Tide in Tremolo mode at 0.6 Hz with small depth for a pulse that mimics a bioluminescent flash rate. Reef at size 0.25 — just enough to place the sound in a physical space without overwhelming the shimmer.",
